snippet.title: Space Duel - Atari 7800 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Captured via Atari 2600+

Originally released as a homebrew game via AtariAge in 2007, this 7800 port of Space Duel was given an official release by Atari in 2024, as part of the launch of the Atari 7800+.
